node.text:
Energy harnessed during the making of @WadeGoodall’s third collection with @Vans.

Here’s Wade, @HollyWawn, and @HarryBryant’s summertime trip through the desert, putting the full range to the test.

🎥 @Fox_in_Soks / @JimmyLees

node.text: Plagued with eggy winds and a junky swell, this wave only broke for two days during our trip. In an attempt to avoid the crowds at this particular reef, @Sealtooth, @WadeGoodall & @TannerGud surfed solely at dead-low tide. 🎥 @ShaneFletcher and @R_Ritchie

node.text:
Eighteen surfers, six Ladybirds, five judges, ten filmers, and twelve days in Costa Rica.

Episode 1 of @Stab_High Central America is live, and free to all! Playing now on stabmag.com and YouTube.

node.text: We’re less than 24 hours from the launch of @Stab_High Central America. Check in with one of the five judges, @Vans_Europe’s @AinarAymat, who laid a heavy focus on style in the air. You can watch the first episode for free on @Stab’s YouTube channel, tomorrow at 7PM PT.
